dct_title_s: Street plan of the city of London
dct_description_sm: Ed. J. Borrow & Co. Ltd. Companion text: The City of London Official Guide / Charles White. Cheltenham & London: Ed. J. Borrow & Co. Ltd. 1953. 8th ed. 264p. Shows bomb damage. Map was part of "The official guide to the city of London", the library does not have a copy of this volume. Map mounted on paper.
